r put on the stack is the first one that resolves. That means that in a two-player game, the nonactive player’s persist creatures will return to the battlefield first, then the active player’s persist creatures do the same. The creatures return to the battlefield one at a time.£6/7/2013: If a creature with persist that has +1/+1 counters on it receives enough -1/-1 counters to cause it to be destroyed by lethal damage or put into its owner’s graveyard for having 0 or less toughness, persist won’t trigger and the card won’t return to the battlefield. That’s because persist checks the creature’s existence just before it leaves the battlefield, and it still has all those counters on it at that point.','W',NULL,'0.25','0.96','6.72',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'W',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),('197001','Unholy Strength','DVD','Enchantment — Aura','C','{B}','1',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Enchant creature£Enchanted creature gets +2/+1.','#_Such power grows the body as it shrinks the soul._#',NULL,'Terese Nielsen','47','3.205',NULL,'B',NULL,'0.05','0.17','1.08',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'B',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),('197002','Venerable Monk','DVD','Creature — Human Monk Cleric','C','{2}{W}','3','2','2',NULL,'When Venerable Monk enters the battlefield, you gain 2 life.','#_Age wears the flesh but galvanizes the soul._#',NULL,'D. Alexander Gregory','5','2.395',NULL,'W',NULL,'0.05','0.18','0.94',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'W',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NUL